project_descr: The project supports trade facilitation in the region of Palanca with the creation of a jointly operated border crossing point (JOBCP) at Palanca, on the territory of Republic of Moldova

outputs.output_descr: The project will build a new jointly operated border crossing point (JOBCP) at Palanca, on the territory of Republic of Moldova (hereinafter Moldova) for improved border crossing of passengers and cargo.

document_name: Construction of the Border Crossing Point Palanca located in Stefan Voda district
Construction of the Border Crossing Point Palanca located in Stefan Voda district: Main facilitie
Preparation works for the Construction of the Border Crossing Point Palanca located in Stefan Voda district, including: Demolition and territory arrangements, grading and leveling works.
Provision of Technical Design Services for the construction of the Palanca Jointly Operated Border Crossing Point
